<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="he" dir="rtl">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>מרכז המשחקים של גיא</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Heebo:wght@400;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #0f4c6b;
      --soft-ink: #4a7a94;
      --glass: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      --line: rgba(160,220,240,0.7);
      --shadow-card: 0 20px 50px rgba(20,80,110,0.13);
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      font-family: "Heebo", "Arial Rounded MT Bold", sans-serif;
      color: var(--ink);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 8% 14%, rgba(255,90,160,0.38) 0%, transparent 22%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 88% 18%, rgba(255,175,90,0.35) 0%, transparent 20%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 76% 80%, rgba(80,210,255,0.28) 0%, transparent 20%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 18% 80%, rgba(140,100,255,0.2) 0%, transparent 18%),
        linear-gradient(145deg, #fff4cc, #ffe0ef 42%, #e6faff 100%);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* floating blobs */
    body::before, body::after {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      border-radius: 50%;
      pointer-events: none;
      filter: blur(40px);
      opacity: 0.55;
      z-index: 0;
      animation: blobFloat 14s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    body::before {
      width: 36vw; height: 36vw;
      top: 2vh; left: 2vw;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,80,160,0.32), transparent 70%);
    }
    body::after {
      width: 30vw; height: 30vw;
      bottom: 4vh; right: 3vw;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,190,70,0.3), transparent 72%);
      animation-delay: -7s;
    }

    .shell {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      width: min(1160px, calc(100% - 28px));
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 26px 0 52px;
    }

    /* ── TOP NAV ── */
    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
      animation: fadeUp 0.5s ease both;
    }

    .nav-logo {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      padding: 11px 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(30,90,120,0.13);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .nav-logo-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd166, #63d8ff, #ff8db4);
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(30,90,120,0.18);
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      gap: 8px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .nav-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 7px;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--ink);
      background: var(--glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(30,90,120,0.09);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      transition: transform 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s;
    }
    .nav-link:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 28px rgba(30,90,120,0.16);
    }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 36px 36px 32px;
      border-radius: 36px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(255,209,102,0.22), transparent 24%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 90% 15%, rgba(100,220,255,0.16), transparent 20%),
        rgba(255,255,255,0.74);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      margin-bottom: 26px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      animation: fadeUp 0.55s 0.05s ease both;
    }

    .hero::after {
      content: "🕹️";
      position: absolute;
      left: -10px;
      bottom: -18px;
      font-size: 9rem;
      opacity: 0.07;
      pointer-events: none;
      transform: rotate(-12deg);
    }

    .hero-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 14px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #edfbff);
      border: 1px solid rgba(190,232,243,0.9);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(30,90,120,0.08);
    }

    .hero-quick {
      display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4.4rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .hero-sub {
      color: var(--soft-ink);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 680px;
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    /* stats row */
    .stats-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .stat-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(190,232,243,0.85);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 18px rgba(30,90,120,0.07);
    }

    .stat-dot {
      width: 10px; height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    /* ── SECTION LABEL ── */
    .section-label {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    .section-label::after {
      content: "";
      flex: 1;
      height: 1px;
      background: var(--line);
    }

    /* ── GAMES GRID ── */
    .games-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .game-card {
      padding: 28px;
      border-radius: 32px;
      background: var(--glass);
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      transition: transform 0.22s ease, box-shadow 0.22s ease;
      cursor: default;
    }

    .game-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.012);
      box-shadow: 0 30px 64px rgba(20,80,110,0.18);
    }

    /* accent glow per card */
    .game-card.card-hangman::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -40px; right: -40px;
      width: 160px; height: 160px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,122,89,0.22), transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .game-card.card-wordle::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: -40px; right: -40px;
      width: 160px; height: 160px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(26,183,200,0.22), transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .card-top {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .card-num {
      display: inline-flex;
      padding: 6px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #edfbff);
      border: 1px solid rgba(190,232,243,0.9);
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }

    .card-emoji {
      width: 60px; height: 60px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: grid; place-items: center;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(30,90,120,0.14);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .card-emoji.hangman-em { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffd166, #ff9c7e); }
    .card-emoji.wordle-em  { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #63d8ff, #5fa8ff); }

    .card-title {
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .card-desc {
      color: var(--soft-ink);
      line-height: 1.65;
      font-size: 0.96rem;
    }

    .chips {
      display: flex; gap: 7px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .chip {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(190,232,243,0.85);
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }

    .features {
      display: grid; gap: 8px;
    }

    .feature {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.68);
      border: 1px solid rgba(190,232,243,0.8);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 9px;
    }

    .feature::before { content: "✦"; color: var(--soft-ink); font-size: 0.7rem; flex-shrink: 0; }

    /* play button */
    .play-btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #fff;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #17c7da, #ffc957);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 30px rgba(255,178,84,0.25);
      transition: transform 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s;
      align-self: flex-start;
    }
    .play-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.02);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 38px rgba(255,178,84,0.35);
    }
    .play-btn::after { content: "→"; }

    /* ── COMING SOON ── */
    .soon-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .soon-card {
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.48);
      border: 1px dashed rgba(160,220,240,0.75);
      display: grid;
      gap: 10px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
    }

    .soon-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.62);
    }

    .soon-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(190,232,243,0.85);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--soft-ink);
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .soon-em {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }

    .soon-title {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .soon-desc {
      color: var(--soft-ink);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--soft-ink);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      opacity: 0.7;
      padding-top: 10px;
    }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    @keyframes blobFloat {
      0%, 100% { transform: translate(0,0) scale(1); }
      50%       { transform: translate(1.5vw,-1.5vh) scale(1.05); }
    }

    .game-card { animation: fadeUp 0.55s ease both; }
    .game-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.12s; }
    .game-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
    .soon-card  { animation: fadeUp 0.55s ease both; }
    .soon-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.28s; }
    .soon-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.34s; }
    .soon-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 800px) {
      .games-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .soon-grid  { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
      .hero { padding: 24px; border-radius: 26px; }
      .game-card { border-radius: 24px; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .soon-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .shell { padding: 18px 0 36px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="shell">

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="nav">
    <div class="nav-logo">
      <div class="nav-logo-icon">🕹️</div>
      מרכז המשחקים של גיא
    </div>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a class="nav-link" href="https://glittery-kitsune-e2b718.netlify.app/hangman-game/index.html">🎯 איש תלוי</a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="https://glittery-kitsune-e2b718.netlify.app/wordle-game/index.html">🔤 וורדל</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-top">
      <div class="hero-badge">✨ שני משחקים חיים כבר בפנים</div>
      <div class="hero-quick">
        <a class="nav-link" href="https://glittery-kitsune-e2b718.netlify.app/hangman-game/index.html">⚡ ישר לאיש תלוי</a>
        <a class="nav-link" href="https://glittery-kitsune-e2b718.netlify.app/wordle-game/index.html">⚡ ישר לוורדל</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1>ברוכים הבאים למרכז<br>המשחקים 🎮</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">כל המשחקים שלך תחת קורף אחד — עם אונליין, טורניר, פרופילים, ועוד המון שמתחבר בהמשך.</p>
    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-pill"><span class="stat-dot" style="background:#22c55e"></span>2 משחקים פעילים</div>
      <div class="stat-pill"><span class="stat-dot" style="background:#f59e0b"></span>3 משחקים בדרך</div>
      <div class="stat-pill">🌐 Netlify</div>
      <div class="stat-pill">⚡ אונליין אמיתי</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LIVE GAMES -->
  <div class="section-label">🟢 משחקים פעילים</div>
  <div class="games-grid">

    <!-- HANGMAN -->
    <article class="game-card card-hangman">
      <div class="card-top">
        <span class="card-num">🎯 משחק 1</span>
        <div class="card-emoji hangman-em">🎯</div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="card-title">איש תלוי</h2>
      <p class="card-desc">משחק ענק עם מצבי סיפור, טורניר, אונליין אמיתי, פרופילים, אתגרים, מוזיקה וגביעים.</p>
      <div class="chips">
        <span class="chip">אונליין</span>
        <span class="chip">סיפור</span>
        <span class="chip">טורניר</span>
        <span class="chip">פרופילים</span>
        <span class="chip">מוזיקה</span>
      </div>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">חדרים אונליין עם קישור שיתוף</div>
        <div class="feature">סיפור, הישרדות, מסיבה ואתגרים</div>
        <div class="feature">גביעים, XP, ולוח שיאים</div>
      </div>
      <a class="play-btn" href="https://glittery-kitsune-e2b718.netlify.app/hangman-game/index.html" target="_blank">פתח איש תלוי</a>
    </article>

    <!-- WORDLE -->
    <article class="game-card card-wordle">
      <div class="card-top">
        <span class="card-num">🔤 משחק 2</span>
        <div class="card-emoji wordle-em">🔤</div>
      </div>
      <h2 class="card-title">וורדל</h2>
      <p class="card-desc">וורדל צבעוני ועשיר — עברית ואנגלית, אתגר יומי, אונליין, טורניר, פרופילים וצלילים.</p>
      <div class="chips">
        <span class="chip">עברית ואנגלית</span>
        <span class="chip">יומי</span>
        <span class="chip">תחרות</span>
        <span class="chip">ילדים</span>
      </div>
      <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">מאגר ענק בעברית ואנגלית</div>
        <div class="feature">אתגר יומי, שבועי ומצב ילדים</div>
        <div class="feature">רמזים, שיאים ואפקטי צליל</div>
      </div>
      <a class="play-btn" href="https://glittery-kitsune-e2b718.netlify.app/wordle-game/index.html" target="_blank">פתח וורדל</a>
    </article>

  </div>

  <!-- COMING SOON -->
  <div class="section-label">🚧 בדרך אליכם</div>
  <div class="soon-grid">

    <div class="soon-card">
      <div class="soon-badge">🐍 בקרוב</div>
      <div class="soon-em">🐍</div>
      <div class="soon-title">Snake</div>
      <div class="soon-desc">נחש קלאסי עם מצבי מהירות, עיצובים מותאמים ולוח שיאים.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="soon-card">
      <div class="soon-badge">🧠 בקרוב</div>
      <div class="soon-em">🧠</div>
      <div class="soon-title">משחק זיכרון</div>
      <div class="soon-desc">התאמת זוגות קלפים עם רמות, טיימר ומצב שני שחקנים.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="soon-card">
      <div class="soon-badge">🧩 בקרוב</div>
      <div class="soon-em">🧩</div>
      <div class="soon-title">טריוויה</div>
      <div class="soon-desc">שאלות בנושאים שונים עם מצב תחרות ואונליין נגד חברים.</div>
    </div>

  </div>

  <div class="footer">עשוי עם ❤️ על ידי גיא · glittery-kitsune-e2b718.netlify.app</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
